tica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100556_13983.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"> 16<o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">狼獾<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">虽然没有正式的统计数字，估计硕果仅存的约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">300</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只，生活在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;m