di-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">德州盲螈<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">总数约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1,150</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">150</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">圈养，野生的估计有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">100</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100517_30231.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20<o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">北极熊<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">估计在阿拉斯加地区有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">3500</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">北极熊居无定所，它们时常往来于俄罗斯海至阿拉斯加的冰面上，此外加拿大、格陵兰和斯瓦尔巴群岛的广阔地带都是它们的家园。北极熊的最大天敌是猎人，北极熊的总体数量约为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">22000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">，目前由于气候变化造成海洋浮冰融化，它们的种群数量在下降，尤其在某些北极地区。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100537_47172.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 21</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">墨西哥斑点猫头鹰<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">估计数量在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">之间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100558_21130.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"> 22<o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">派恩</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:arial;mso-ascii-font-family:arial;mso-hansi-font-family:arial;\">青梅</span><o :p></o :p></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">估计在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">2500</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">3000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">株之间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100527_81990.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">23<o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span class=\"wbtrmn1\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:arial;mso-hansi-font-family:arial;\">佛州地鼠陆龟</span></span><span class=\"wbtrmn1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">该物种生活在美国东南部，但结局往往很悲惨。其卵和幼龟也是外来红火蚁和犰狳的捕食对象，同时随着城市的日益扩张，它们的栖息地不仅被变成了松树种植园，而且由于防火不善而遭到破坏，目前这些爬行动物正处于灭绝的边缘。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100544_67213.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 24</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">阿拉巴马海滩鼠<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">阿拉巴马海滩鼠活跃在美国摩根堡半岛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">英里长的海滩，然而它们栖息的沙丘被建筑物代替，而且夜间灯火通明。现在濒危物种法案正在保护这些昼伏夜出的动物免遭与渡渡鸟同样的厄运。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100501_77868.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 25</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">加州</span><span class=\"wbtrmn1\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:arial;mso-hansi-font-family:arial;\">秃鹰</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">336</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">156</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">野生，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">180</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只人工</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">圈养）。它们是冰河时代幸存下来的产物，但却无法逃脱人类的毒手。这些大自然的拾荒者不是遭到猎人枪杀，就是因为品尝猎人投下的毒物而一命呜呼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1985</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">年普查到的野生</span><span class=\"wbtrmn1\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:arial;mso-hansi-font-family:arial;\">秃鹰只有硕果仅存的</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只。目前，由于人工繁殖和铅质弹药的减少使用，该物种有起死回生的迹象。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100531_88614.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 26</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">美国填埋甲虫<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">仅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">25,000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只。这种</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">甲虫喜欢生活在黑暗、不受干扰且动物死尸富足的地区。它们是大自然的搬运工，习惯于为后代储藏动物的死尸。它们在美国现身的范围已经从曾经的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">35</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">个州下降到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">个州，同时数量</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">也在下降。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100552_83184.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 27</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">林地驯鹿<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">曾经生活在美国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">48</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">个州低洼地区的林地驯鹿目前仅存</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">40</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头。它们习惯于生活在年代悠久</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">的森林里，目前仅数量有限的林地驯鹿还从加拿大向北进入美国爱达荷州和华盛顿地区。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100513_17139.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 28<o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">美洲鹤<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">数量约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">538</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">387</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">野生，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">151</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只人工</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">圈养）。人工孵化、迁徙驯化等多种手段正在拯救美洲鹤于绝迹。然而令人不安的局面并没有改变：美洲鹤迁徙沿线的城市化发展让这一已经稀少的物种恢复得更加艰难。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100530_66945.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 29<o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">灰熊<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">生活在美国<span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span>个州的低洼地区，估计约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1,500</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">由于有关管理部门的干预，灰熊的数量正在恢复上升，同时野生动物保护专家们正在下功夫，准备把洛矶山北部地区的灰熊栖息地重新连成一片。灰熊的命运差点儿断送在人类手中，据蒙大拿州灰熊专家克里斯·塞福恩估计，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1920</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1940</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">年之间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">48</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">个州低地发现的灰熊</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">不到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">300</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100548_25328.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"> 30<o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">牟氏龟<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">总计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">18,100</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">（估计数量在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">14,500</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">18,100</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只之间</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">）。这种巴掌大的沼泽龟是美国最小的龟，目前绝大多数生存在私人领地。它们适合生活在潮湿地区，由于湿地被填埋，或地下水改道，它们遭到了灭顶之灾。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100508_47258.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 31</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">圣安德鲁</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">海滩鼠<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">剩余</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">6000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">（估计数量在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">3500</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">6000</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">只之间</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">世界不会因为少了它们而崩溃，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">生物学家桑德拉斯奈克博格指出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">但它们是生态系统健康的晴雨表。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">随着</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">美国佛罗里达州海边沙丘不断变成公共或私人领地，圣安德鲁海滩鼠正在失去自己的栖息地，它们的</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">数量开始岌岌可危</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">。如果上述双方能够携手努力，海滩鼠的命运也许会柳暗花明。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-05/25/20100525100526_68061.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">图<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 32</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">墨西哥灰狼<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">320</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">60</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头生活在野外</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">，人工圈养</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">260</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-ascii-font-family:verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:verdana;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">头</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">）。作为一个濒危亚种，墨西哥灰狼的地位岌岌可危。不过由于人工繁殖的功劳，亚利桑那州和新墨西哥州地区该物种的数量正在缓慢上升。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">本文刊登于2010-05-25《网易探索》</font></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">链接：<a href=\"http://news.163.com/photonew/05RQ0001/9353.html\">http://news.163.com/photonew/05RQ0001/9353.html</a></font></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><o :p></o :p></font></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;\"><o :p></o :p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o :p></o :p></span></font></span></p> <p><a hr